                     <interp inst="t17760221-19-off99" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17760221-19-off99" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               they, in the king's highway, in and upon 
                     
                        <persName id="t17760221-19-victim242" type="victimName">
